data.Name: Rumors (A Tribute to Fleetwood Mac)
data.Description: If you decide to keep your ticket for the new date, please come join us for FREE ADMISSION tonight! HOLD ON TO THOSE TICKETS and see you in October for the Fleetwood Mac show!The Show Will Go On TONIGHT! Purple Blues, and special guest Ben Pu will still be performing live at the Moxi Theater tonight! Purple blues is erik Truchses, Spenser Dunn, Emily nelson with special guest Greg Heimbecker. We regret to inform you that a member of Rumours: Fleetwood Mac Tribute Band has been exposed to Covid and out of an abundance of caution, the band has elected to reschedule the date for October 8th, 2022. Tickets will be honored for the new date, refunds are available if you cannot attend the new date. Moxi Theater is operating at Full CapacityReserve a Table in Advance Online.All Responsible Ages Permitted*PHOTO ID REQUIRED FOR ENTRYThe Moxi Theater is proudly partnered with Lunas Tacos s is located at 806 9th St. - next door to the Moxi and is open for Dinner, Happy Hour, and Late Night. Lunas is the perfect place to eat and drink before or after the show!Stellas Pinball Arcade s directly beneath the Moxi before the show. Now serving Burgers, Apps, Cocktails, Icees, and fun for all ages. Open 6 days a week!
